{#
OPTIMIZED:
- This approach gets rid of the individual twig templates for icons.
- Use one twig template to generate any SVGs.
Requirement:
- svg file and id need to match. --- in this case no sprite.

Mayflower: /assets/
Drupal: /themes/custom/mass_theme/

